<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-20 16:59 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2837 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f BC-ECOMMERCE-COLUMN-ART-     02-20 1119
