<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-20 20:53 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2958 &Cx1f; taf-z
u p BC-REPUBS-FINANCES-NYT &LR;      02-20 0804
