<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-20 21:46 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2989 &Cx1f; tta-z
u p BC-MICH-REPUBS-1STLD-WRI     02-20 1024
