County city of Oceanside. ``We were getting called out at 1 in the
morning to reset a password.'' But since last year, the 1,200 city
employees have been logging on to the computer network using
something they can't forget _ their fingers.  &UR; BY &LR; 
 &UR; BENNY EVANGELISTA &LR;
